## remoteConfig.Version interface

Interface representing a Remote Config template version. Output only, except for the version description. Contains metadata about a particular version of the Remote Config template. All fields are set at the time the specified Remote Config template is published. A version's description field may be specified in `publishTemplate` calls.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
interface Version 
```

## Properties

|  Property | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  [description](./firebase-admin.remoteconfig.version.description.md) | string | The user-provided description of the corresponding Remote Config template. |
|  [isLegacy](./firebase-admin.remoteconfig.version.islegacy.md) | boolean | Indicates whether this Remote Config template was published before version history was supported. |
|  [rollbackSource](./firebase-admin.remoteconfig.version.rollbacksource.md) | string | The version number of the Remote Config template that has become the current version due to a rollback. Only present if this version is the result of a rollback. |
|  [updateOrigin](./firebase-admin.remoteconfig.version.updateorigin.md) | ('REMOTE\_CONFIG\_UPDATE\_ORIGIN\_UNSPECIFIED' \| 'CONSOLE' \| 'REST\_API' \| 'ADMIN\_SDK\_NODE') | The origin of the template update action. |
|  [updateTime](./firebase-admin.remoteconfig.version.updatetime.md) | string | The timestamp of when this version of the Remote Config template was written to the Remote Config backend. |
|  [updateType](./firebase-admin.remoteconfig.version.updatetype.md) | ('REMOTE\_CONFIG\_UPDATE\_TYPE\_UNSPECIFIED' \| 'INCREMENTAL\_UPDATE' \| 'FORCED\_UPDATE' \| 'ROLLBACK') | The type of the template update action. |
|  [updateUser](./firebase-admin.remoteconfig.version.updateuser.md) | [RemoteConfigUser](./firebase-admin.remoteconfig.remoteconfiguser.md) | Aggregation of all metadata fields about the account that performed the update. |
|  [versionNumber](./firebase-admin.remoteconfig.version.versionnumber.md) | string | The version number of a Remote Config template. |
